      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cook, covered, for 5-7 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!), the sauce has thickened and the tomatoes are starting to break down</p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>harissa & tomato chicken</strong></p><p>Fluff the <strong>couscous</strong> with a fork</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
