    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>harissa & tomato chicken</strong> with the <strong>couscous </strong>to the side</p><p>Dollop with the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
